Superteam Vietnam & @dephynetwork: Decentralizing IoT in Hanoi

🚀 Calling all IoT builders!

Join us on February 7 in Hanoi, Vietnam for an exclusive dinner hosted by Superteam Vietnam and DePHY’s CEO. This event is dedicated to empowering IoT developers and entrepreneurs to explore how DePIN (Decentralized Physical Infrastructure Networks) can revolutionize their businesses and unlock new revenue streams.

Whether you’re building smart locks, cameras, or other IoT solutions, this is your chance to learn how decentralization can transform your projects—whether you’re working in web2 or web3!

What’s in it for you?

✨ Inspiring Discussions
Dive deep into how DePIN mechanisms can decentralize IoT systems and create new earning opportunities.

💡 Success Stories
Explore real-world use cases and practical examples of DePIN in action across IoT industries.

🤝 Networking Opportunities
Connect with IoT builders, innovators, and industry leaders to exchange ideas and collaborate.

🔑 Actionable Insights
Walk away with a clear understanding of how to integrate DePIN into your IoT solutions.

This is your chance to join a movement reshaping the future of IoT through decentralization.

📅 When: February 7, 2025
📍 Where: Hanoi, Vietnam
🔗 Register here: https://t.co/L51isx7kBF

Don’t miss out—spaces are limited! 👾

🚀 BIG NEWS ALERT! 🚀

We’re super duper hyped to announce that @windexer_sol has bagged a $7,000 grant to build a peer-to-peer data indexing network for @solana! 🎉

But why does this matter?
Accessing on-chain data on Solana is crazy expensive and only getting pricier because of the high entry barriers to becoming a validator. This doesn’t just cost $$—it stifles innovation. 😟

Think about it: Love tools like @Sonarwatch or @get_nimbus? Same here! But do you know how much it costs these legends to keep your dashboards running? And how many cool projects never see daylight because the cost to serve this data is just too damn high?

Enter @vivekpal0x and @windexer_sol!
He is building a peer-to-peer network to make on-chain data affordable and accessible, powered by indexers secured with @jito_sol’s (re)stacking tech.

🗓 Mark your calendars: A demo + small-scale network is coming 31 March!
📜 Full pitch deck link in the comments.

If you’re as excited as we are:
👉 DM @vivekpal0x, follow @windexer_sol, and join his working group.
👉 Are you a builder with a dream? Submit to the @supertean Instagrant and grab your 💵 to make it happen!

Innovation shouldn’t be a luxury. Let’s change the game. 💪
@windexer_sol @solana Pitch deck: https://t.co/O6deMjj7Tp
@windexer_sol @solana Developer working docs: https://t.co/dXMY7IAlwc

🚀 Excited to announce my role as @Solana @SuperteamVN lead! Superteam is the talent layer of Solana, and I’m committed to driving success for every member & founder. Projects may come and go, but as long as talent stays, Solana will thrive!

In 2022, @SuperteamVN was the underdog. I’m deeply grateful to @SaigonButcher @mmthach for their hard work in building a close-knit community that’s generated millions in GDP & investments. With other superteam members, my mission is to accelerate Superteam Vietnam in 2025.

My 2025 vision:
1️⃣ Attract top-tier talent & institutional partners into the Solana ecosystem.
2️⃣ Empower members to succeed—from founders accessing capital & acceleration to individuals finding clear pathways and studios securing bootstrapping contracts.
3️⃣ Grow beyond Hanoi & HCMC by establishing a Web3 building & living hub in Da Nang—a sunny, high-quality haven for web3 nomads building in Vietnam.

Let’s work together to make 2025 a landmark year for @SuperteamVN and the Solana ecosystem. 🌟

#BuildWithSolana #SuperteamVietnam

Me in 2024
- Joined @SuperteamVN as devrel.
- Hosted various tech workshops.
- Joined renaissance, radar (w/@purr_fect_sol) (failed).
- First trip to Malaysia & Singapore.
- Founded @weship_hq.
- Won Talent Olympics
- Followed by @solana .
- Landed first web3 job
